% Employment Section
\section*{RESEARCH EXPERIENCE}
\noindent
\newline
\noindent
\textbf{Contemporary Jewellery: improving well-being and quality of life} \\
Year: 2024 \\
Seminar\\ 
The core issues of this seminar include but are not limited to what circumstances, how the wearing of jewelry can improve people's mood and health, how to use the power of jewelry to express personal identity and create happiness properly, and how to enhance the value and improve our quality of life through the redesign and innovation of jewelry.\\

\noindent
\textbf{Deconstruction of Lipstick Names: Research on Marketing Linguistics from the Perspective of Contemporary Chinese Female Consumers} \\
Year: 2024 \\
Research\\ 
Based on the analysis of lipstick naming strategies of major cosmetics brands, including language style, color vocabulary, graphic symbols, and other elements, this study further explores the direct impact of lipstick names on consumers, as well as the emotional responses and psychological expectations it may trigger, and ultimately affect consumers' purchase choices through field survey, questionnaire survey, interview, and other data. The research hopes to provide precise and targeted marketing strategies for the cosmetics industry. \\

\noindent
\textbf{2024 Chinese overseas study agency market research} \\
Year:2024 \\
Research\\
Based on preliminary data analysis and the characteristics of the overseas study market, this in-depth study on China's overseas study agency market constructs detailed research hypotheses and verifies them. This study will help companies better understand market dynamics, customer needs, and service effectiveness, and guide intermediaries to optimize services and expand the market. \\

\noindent
\textbf{The Construction and Communication of Fashion Brand} \\
Year: 2023 \\
Program\\ 
Knew the brand and marketing strategy planning of fashion and luxury; Understood how to inspire purchase desire and establish trust through marketing, communication, and sales channels to achieve the vision and strategic goals of luxury brands; Explored marketing studies in brand construction and acquired practical skills such as field investigation, interview investigation, and questionnaire survey, etc. \\

